section.def:
clerk
                (書記) means the clerk to a Tribunal or any person
            appointed by a Tribunal to perform the duties of that office;

inquiry
                (研訊) means an inquiry under section
                40J(1) of the Ordinance;

respondent
                (答辯人) means a notary public whose conduct is the
            subject of an inquiry;

Secretary
                (秘書) means the Secretary of the Society of
            Notaries;

Tribunal
                (審裁組) means a Notaries Public Disciplinary
            Tribunal constituted under section 40I of the Ordinance;
